creator: Yea Studio. Co., Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
One peaceful day, a thief sneaked into the farm and stole the sheep!
Hurry up and help the farmer to get the sheep back!
Blast blocks and obstacles, and the adventure begins to find the stolen sheep!
Make it easier with boosters!


[HOW TO PLAY]
• Tap 2 or more blocks of the same color to break them!
• Tap 5 blocks to create a booster that can explode all blocks in a horizontal or vertical row.
• Tap 6 blocks to create Dynamite that can burst all blocks in the surrounding 8 spaces.
• Tap 7 or more blocks to create a Rainbow Bomb that can burst all blocks of the same color.


[SPECIAL FEATURES]
• Various levels, various boosters!
• No Wifi - anytime, anywhere!
• Easy and relaxing, the perfect experience!
• Optimized play on smartphones and tablets!


E-MAIL
• help@yeastudio.net
descriptionShort: Let's get the sheep back with a puzzle match game!
